Subject: scsi: lpfc: Move initialization of phba->poll_list earlier to avoid
 crash
Patch-mainline: v5.14-rc6
Git-commit: 9977d880f7a3c233db9165a75a3a14defc2a4aee
References: git-fixes

The phba->poll_list is traversed in case of an error in
lpfc_sli4_hba_setup(), so it must be initialized earlier in case the error
path is taken.

